commit_message:
Add ability to configure AVAILABLE_REGIONS

Example on how to use this setting:

  class { 'horizon':
    available_regions => [
      ['http://region-1.example.com:5000/v2.0', 'Region-1'],
      ['http://region-2.example.com:5000/v2.0', 'Region-2']
    ]
  }

